							<h5>Release Advisory</h5>
							<p>All films or any audio-visual product need adequate release because it has to reach its audiences and recover its investments. Releasing a film is an intricate process and due to the changing dynamics and business metrics of today’s rapidly evolving market, it has become all the more cumbersome. We engage in careful devising of fine strategy on the release of your film starting with the most important decision of finalising a suitable date for the release of your film which entails a lot of thinking, planning and strategy. Designing communication, and strategy for marketing, planning the entire campaign calendar for you, which constitutes the revelation of teasers, posters, trailers and promos as well as the total marketing thinking around the film across diverse media platforms. A well released product with complete background planning is a battle half won.  </p>
                             <h5>Distribution</h5>
							<p>Depending on the reach, scale, budget and quality of the film, we can plan its worldwide release or even an Indian one. Distribution is critical as it directly impacts your important 3 Rs - Reach, Reaction and Revenue. A well distributed film is likely to recover costs and get the producer and the minds behind the film well known in the realm of audiences, media as well as critics. Distribution entails, number of screens, territories and countries to where the film can have an audience, and market interest. Also the business considerations are kept in mind vis-à-vis the ROI (Return on Investment). With wide ranging distribution network and a penchant to understand the nature, content and other metrics of a film, we are just about the right team to consult with. 
We at H 2 B have tied up with M/s. Triveni Films promoted by Sanjay Kaul and have distributed more than 700 films . The prominent movies among these have been:
<B> Deewaar, Trishul, Mohra, Gupt, Laadla, Phool aur Kaante, Sholay, Satyamev Jayte, Dilwale Dulhaniya Le Jayenge, Kaala Pathar, Daag, Johny Mera Naam, Shaan, Naagin, Nagina, Tridev, Kabhie Kabhie, Dostana Jaadugar, Toofan, Aai (Marathi ), Chimni Pakhre (Marathi), Toofan, Jigar, Ek Duje Ke Liye, Rocky,Karz, Dayavan, Shortcut, Safari, Game of Ayodhya, Murari, Braveheart (Marathi), Sabrang, Dream job, Saptshringi, Mata (Marathi), Ashtrawakra (Marathi), Twin Mission (English ), Eyewitness (English), Langda Martay Tangda (Marathi) Shaadi Abhi Baaki Hai, Viraam, Mr Kabaadi,  Chalu Dya Tumcha (Marathi),  Dil Hi toh Hai, Don Baika Fajiti Aika (Marathi), Ashley,  My Father Iqbal, Rastraputra, H2O (Marathi), Kahi Kshan Premache (Marathi), Phallat (Marathi), Phir Usi Mod Par Talaq, Tattad ( Marathi). </B>


.</p>
							 <h5>Marketing </h5>
							<p>As in any business, marketing assumes incomparable importance. Strategic marketing  (or thoughtfully designed marketing)  is the tool which makes your product get noticed by audiences. It caters to their demographic reality and psychographic taste. In a world of in your face aggressive media, marketing has assumed great significance today as it not only creates awareness but defines opinion making and therefore creating word of mouth and even viral promotions. It is the edifice around which the excitement around your film is created for the audience so that they spend going to the theatres to consume your offer. We define your films target audience, their psychographics and demographics and manage the entire mark comm strategy and its execution so that we can reach the farthest mile and create the right kind of awareness about your soon to be released film. Across the gamut of media, we channelize our acumen to get you the maximum bang for your buck. TV, Social Media, OOH, Print, Trade, POS, we take a measured parameter for every option, and strategize our thoughts and pockets and adapt our marketing communication strategies accordingly.  We also lend you free city promotional tour plans for the stars to promote their film. </p>
							 <h5>Digital Marketing</h5>
							<p>Digital is the name of the game today. Digital is where every business is going and where the reach, reaction and revenues are impacted. Digital is where design, dynamics and decorum is and what is bridging every kind of social, political and economic divide making information democratic to societies across the world. Digital is where you get the maximum eyeballs and therefore maximum bang for your buck. We offer digital solutions to the entertainment industry. With a highly dynamic and pre-emptive skilled team of social media experts and digital wizards, we ensure that your film is reaching the correct audience and garnering maximum eyeballs and beats of excitement. 
							 <h5>Syndication </h5>
							<p>Partnerships and alliances is where we leverage maximum reach and revenue and this is done through multi-pronged syndication. We have a great experience of syndication. We go to great lengths of our network and global market collaborations to get you the optimum mix of generating maximum revenues for your film beyond the customary box office collections. We have in touch with the trade of satellite, music, overseas, digital, mobile, and many other rights that you as a producer should reap the benefit from and we bring that expertise to the table for your benefit. As a production house we have a tie up with all major channels and media platforms and entertainment streams in India which includes regional platforms and around the world as well. Be it Disney, Sony, Star, HBO, Zee, Viacom, 21st Century, Fox, Netflix, Bigflix, Box TV, Ditto TV, Sony Liv, Amazon Prime, Eros Now, Time Warner, we have every major entertainment media stream in India and abroad to hook you up so that your film gets the maximum mileage both in terms of viewership and revenue stream. We also cater to the various OTT platforms which are streaming content to a diverse audience. We recognise the fact that entertainment has become a global business and it is our passion to connect your product globally. </p>

							 <h5>Post Production</h5>
							<p>With state-of-the-art post production facilities and the entire range of jobs in the realm of post-production, we engage in getting your post production done if there is a requirement. We engage in the whole gamut of production and post production of audio-visual products such as documentaries, features, ad films, web series, soaps, music videos and all kinds of animated storytelling. We are experts in getting the promos done as we have a creative team which overlooks the content of the story. We are fully equipped for sound, folly, BG score, music, VFX and animation. Whatever the scale of your film, we are here to provide post production services in its entirety. So come to us, be it any need of your audio-visual dream. We believe, talent can win you games but it is only teamwork which wins championships. </p>

							 <h5>P&A Support </h5>
							<p>P&A (Print & Advertisements) is the backbone of any project. It is the armoury which takes your film around the world by creating awareness and interest generation through media. At H 2 B, we play an important role in bringing you suitable P&A partners as stakeholders in your project. We lend our producers the most apt P&A support, to get the most profitable and judicious mix of commerce and the most efficient combination to promote your film with the right kind of backing and budget so that it reaches the intended target market and meets your financial recoveries. </p>
